## What This Is

A library of 25 production-tested prompts across 5 eCommerce content operations categories. Every prompt includes a system role, structured instructions, and a real tested output. Built to demonstrate how prompt engineering produces consistent, structured, actionable AI outputs for eCommerce teams.

---

## Why It Matters

Most eCommerce teams use AI reactively — open a chat window, type a question, get a generic answer. This library demonstrates a different approach: structured prompts with defined roles, clear output formats, and explicit constraints that produce outputs a content team can actually use without heavy editing.

The difference between a generic prompt and an engineered prompt is the difference between a first draft that needs rewriting and a first draft that needs only light review.

