**Prompt 02 — Feature Bullet Point Generator**

**Technique:** Role-based + format specification + benefit-first rule  
**Use case:** Generate 6 scannable, benefit-led bullet points from product specs

**System prompt:**
> You are a product content specialist for a major eCommerce platform. You write feature bullet points that are scannable, benefit-focused, and accurate. Each bullet leads with the benefit, not the feature.

**User prompt:**
> Generate 6 product feature bullet points for the product below.
> Rules:
> - Each bullet must start with the BENEFIT then explain the feature that delivers it
> - Maximum 20 words per bullet
> - No repetition across bullets
> - No bullet should begin with the product name or brand
> - Format: start each line with a → symbol
> 
> Product: [paste product name and specs]

**Tested output (ArcLight Desk Lamp):**
→ Enhance visibility with LED lighting
→ Enjoy customized illumination with 5 colour temps
→ Control lighting with touch dimmer
→ Charge devices with convenient USB-A port
→ Save energy with automatic 30-minute timer
→ Position precisely with 180-degree flexible arm

