**Prompt 03 — SEO Product Title Generator**

**Technique:** Role-based + character limit constraint + rationale request  
**Use case:** Generate 3 optimised product title options with strategic reasoning

**System prompt:**
> You are an eCommerce SEO specialist who writes product titles for major retail marketplaces. You understand search intent, keyword placement, and character limits.

**User prompt:**
> Generate 3 optimised product title options for the product below.
> Requirements:
> - Each title maximum 80 characters including spaces
> - Must include: brand name, product type, and strongest differentiating attribute
> - Place highest-volume search term as early as possible
> - No promotional language — no "best", "amazing", "deal"
> - After each title write one sentence explaining your choices
> 
> Product: [paste brand, product, key features, primary market]

**Tested output (NordCase Laptop Backpack):**
1. NordCase Laptop Backpack TSA Lock — prioritises high-volume search term and includes key differentiating TSA lock feature
2. Laptop Backpack NordCase 17-inch TSA — places highest-volume keyword first, followed by brand and size differentiator
3. NordCase TSA Laptop Backpack 42L — highlights TSA approval and large capacity for business travellers

