> For each market provide:
> - Key tone adjustment needed (2 sentences)
> - Any specifications needing unit conversion
> - Any cultural context to add or remove
> - One phrase from the original to rewrite and why
> 
> Markets: [list markets]
> Original description: [paste description]

**Tested output (SlimStack Knife Block — USA, Germany, Japan):**
