> - 5 high-volume head keywords (broad, high competition)
> - 5 mid-volume body keywords (more specific, medium competition)
> - 5 long-tail keywords (very specific, lower competition, higher conversion intent)
> - 3 negative keywords to exclude from paid campaigns
