## Prompt Engineering Techniques Used

| Technique | Prompts Using It | What It Does |
|---|---|---|
| Role-based prompting | All 25 | Sets domain expertise and output standard |
| Negative constraints | 01, 03, 10 | Prevents generic outputs by explicitly excluding weak patterns |
| Structured output format | 06, 07, 08, 09 | Forces parseable, consistent outputs |
| JSON output instruction | 06 | Enables programmatic use of AI outputs |
| Rationale requirement | 03, 07 | Makes reasoning transparent and auditable |
| PASS/FAIL verdict | 13, 15 | Creates binary accountability for quality and compliance |
| RAG status format | 22, 23 | Standardises risk communication for stakeholders |
| Word/character limits | 02, 04, 10, 22 | Controls output length for specific use cases |
| Chain-of-thought | 16, 17, 18 | Forces analytical reasoning before conclusions |

