## How to Use This Library

1. Copy the system prompt into the system role field of your AI platform
2. Copy the user prompt and replace the bracketed placeholder with your actual product data
3. Run the prompt and review the output against the tested example
4. Adjust the constraints (word count, format, tone) to match your specific requirements

All prompts tested on Claude (primary) and cross-validated on ChatGPT and Groq (Llama 3.3-70b).

